script.name: setup.cycrow.guilds
script.sourceplaintext:
$page.id = 9620 set global variable: name='pageid.guilds' value=$page.id load text: id=$page.id
$read.text = read text: page=$page.id id=99 set mod name display: $read.text
$game.start.group = get game start group id do if $game.start.group == 100 return null
do if does script exist: plugin.manager.waretext @ START [THIS] -> call script plugin.manager.waretext : Text ID=$page.id
@ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.loadconfig : Force=[FALSE] @ $main.universe = [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.utils : type='mainUniverse' Value1=null Value 2=null
@ START [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.donoto :
* create guild data $version = get script version $data = get global variable: name='guilds.data' if not $data $data = table alloc $data['version'] = $version
* do one time init $sector = get sector from universe index: x=22, y=3 if $sector -> exists $flying.ware = Destroyer $main.type = get maintype of ware $flying.ware $sub.type = get subtype of ware $flying.ware $flying.ware = create flying ware: maintype=$main.type subtype=$sub.type count=1 sector=$sector x=-21000 y=7500 z=40000 selfdestruct=0 $flying.ware ->set flying ware as blueprint: [TRUE] $flying.ware ->set discovery points: points=30000 $flying.ware ->set invincible: enabled=[TRUE] $flying.ware ->set LFL target: [TRUE], range=200000 end
set global variable: name='guilds.data' value=$data
* adjust pirate/yaki relations $array = get ship array: of race Pirates class/type=Ship gosub sub.NeutralRelation $array = get ship array: of race Yaki class/type=Ship gosub sub.NeutralRelation $array = get station array: of race Pirates class/type=Station gosub sub.NeutralRelation $array = get station array: of race Yaki class/type=Station gosub sub.NeutralRelation
$table = table alloc $table[Special Discovery] = 100 $table[Maja Snails] = 20 $table[Glowing Crystal] = 20 $table[Black Crystal] = 50 $table[Transparent Crystal] = 100 $table[Yellow Crystal] = 250 $table[Green Crystal] = 500 $table[Blue Crystal] = 1000 $table[Red Crystal] = 2500 $table[Quantum Processor] = 30 $table[Focus Crystal] = 30 @ START [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.addtoasteroid : Items Table=$table Exclusive=[FALSE] Discovery Points=[TRUE]
@ START [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.sectors : Object=null Event='init' Param=null Param2=null
$engine = script engine version if $engine <= 70 $tmp = 'asteroid' @ START [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.patch : Version=$tmp Delay=5000 end
* check if the data is an older version else $check.version = $data['version'] if $version > $check.version $update.version = $check.version while $version > $update.version inc $update.version = @ = [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.patch : Version=$update.version end $data['version'] = $version end end
$guild.data = $data * Initilise the Guilds Data @ START [THIS] -> call script plugin.guilds.init : Guilds Data=$data
* Setup Repair Drones add custom drone: ware=Repair Drone, shiptype=Repair Drone, default command=COMMAND_REPAIR_TARGET set dock type to military: Pirate Military Base register drone carrier: shiptype=Kuiper dronetype=Drone Sentinel
* Setup Races add race flags: race=Corporation 2, flags=[RaceFlg.Inactive] add race flags: race=Race 2, flags=[RaceFlg.Inactive] add race flags: race=Privateer, flags=[RaceFlg.FixedNoto] add race flags: race=Privateer, flags=[RaceFlg.NPC] add race flags: race=Privateer, flags=[RaceFlg.Organised] add race flags: race=Privateer, flags=[RaceFlg.Piloted] add race flags: race=Privateer, flags=[RaceFlg.PilotSub] add race flags: race=Privateer, flags=[RaceFlg.HasEconomy] remove race flags: race=Privateer, flags=2097152 remove race flags: race=Beryll, flags=2097152 add race flags: race=Beryll, flags=[RaceFlg.NPC] remove race flags: race=Industritech, flags=2097152 add race flags: race=Industritech, flags=[RaceFlg.NPC] remove race flags: race=Pioneer, flags=2097152 remove race flags: race=Pioneer, flags=[RaceFlg.Inactive] add race flags: race=Pioneer, flags=[RaceFlg.HasEconomy] add race flags: race=Pioneer, flags=[RaceFlg.NPC] add race flags: race=Pioneer, flags=[RaceFlg.Organised] add race flags: race=Pioneer, flags=[RaceFlg.Terran] $race = Pioneer $race -> set corporation connected race: Terran *$race -> set corporation speaker race: Terran set notoriety of Privateer -> Player to [Notoriety.Max] points set notoriety of Privateer -> Argon to [Notoriety.Neutral] points set notoriety of Argon -> Privateer to [Notoriety.Neutral] points set notoriety of Pioneer -> Terran to [Notoriety.Max] points set notoriety of Terran -> Pioneer to [Notoriety.Max] points
set race welcome message: race=Privateer, textid=17001 set race voice id: race=Privateer, id=115 set race welcome message: race=Pioneer, textid=17002 set race voice id: race=Pioneer, id=129 set race rank page: race=Pioneer, page=842
* Setup luxury wares set ware flags: ware=Fine Wine flags=[WareType.Luxury] set ware flags: ware=Video Games flags=[WareType.Luxury] set ware flags: ware=Motion Simulators flags=[WareType.Luxury] set ware flags: ware=Precious Metals flags=[WareType.Luxury] set ware flags: ware=Tobacco flags=[WareType.Luxury] set ware flags: ware=Clothing flags=[WareType.Luxury] set ware flags: ware=Jewellery flags=[WareType.Luxury] set ware flags: ware=Personal Computer flags=[WareType.Luxury] set ware flags: ware=Sculptures flags=[WareType.Luxury] set ware flags: ware=Paintings flags=[WareType.Luxury] set ware flags: ware=Universal Translators flags=[WareType.Luxury] set ware flags: ware=Medications flags=[WareType.Luxury] set ware flags: ware=Sporting Equipment flags=[WareType.Luxury] set ware flags: ware=Holographic Projectors flags=[WareType.Luxury] set ware flags: ware=Luxury Foodstuffs flags=[WareType.Luxury] set ware flags: ware=Narcotics flags=[WareType.Luxury]
* set illegal wares $array = create new array, size=2, elements=Priest Petals, Discreet Package, null, null, null, null, null, null $i = size of array $array while $i dec $i = $ware = $array[$i] set illegal ware: ware=$ware race=Argon illegal=[TRUE] set illegal ware: ware=$ware race=Boron illegal=[TRUE] set illegal ware: ware=$ware race=Split illegal=[TRUE] set illegal ware: ware=$ware race=Paranid illegal=[TRUE] set illegal ware: ware=$ware race=Teladi illegal=[TRUE] set illegal ware: ware=$ware race=Terran illegal=[TRUE] set illegal ware: ware=$ware race=Pioneer illegal=[TRUE] set illegal ware: ware=$ware race=OTAS illegal=[TRUE] set illegal ware: ware=$ware race=Atreus illegal=[TRUE] set illegal ware: ware=$ware race=NMMC illegal=[TRUE] set illegal ware: ware=$ware race=TerraCorp illegal=[TRUE] set illegal ware: ware=$ware race=Goner illegal=[TRUE] set illegal ware: ware=$ware race=Industritech illegal=[TRUE] end
